{"items":[{"id":"1668360","user":{"id":"1586853902","nickname":"HEITZH","avatar_url":"https://public-static-edu.codemao.cn/17/sdk_upload/1721732485506/d2ViXzEwMDFfNjY5MTQxMzkyXzY2OTE0MTM5Ml8xNzAxODcxMDg3MDkyXzhkMDBkMDhl.jpeg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>考古</p>","n_comments":1,"updated_at":1698580929,"created_at":1698580929,"earliest_comments":[{"id":"2028443","user":{"id":"1636405065","nickname":"大姐牛","avatar_url":"https://public-static-edu.codemao.cn/17/sdk_upload/1725085672747/默认头像.jpg","subject_id":27032,"work_shop_name":"方寸之间","work_shop_level":2,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"考古","created_at":1698580962}]},{"id":"1668339","user":{"id":"243947","nickname":"一只胖达","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_08.jpg","subject_id":23090,"work_shop_name":"胖达工作室","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><strong>函数：</strong> \n<p><strong>函数可以对主要积木进行封装，在需要使用的位置进行相应的使用，可以把脚本缩短。</strong></p> \n<p><strong>函数的优势在于重复的逻辑只需要写一次，即可实现复用。</strong></p> \n<ol> \n <li><strong>定义函数</strong></li> \n</ol> \n<p><strong>可以通过加号和减号增删参数</strong>&nbsp;<strong>函数定义下可以拼接需要的积木，</strong><strong>实现相对应的功能</strong>&nbsp;</p> \n<p><strong>举个例子：</strong></p> \n<p>我们定义一个函数为：画正方形，然后封装画正方形需要用到的积木块。</p> \n<p>这样，我们就只需要用这一块已经封装好的函数积木，来画出正方形，不需要每一次使用都用那么多积木。</p> \n<ol> \n <li><strong>函数参数</strong></li> \n</ol> \n<p><strong>该积木只能在定义函数积木下使用，可以理解成在定义函数积木里面存在的一个变量；</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p> \n<p><strong>这个变量存储着一个数据，是在函数调用的时候传入的，且这个参数在积木定义里</strong><strong>不可以更改</strong><strong>。</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p> \n<p><strong>提示：</strong></p> \n<p>需要注意的是，<strong>“参数”积木不会出现在积木盒子中</strong>，使用时直接从其所属的【定义函数】积木中拖拽出来，即可与其他积木结合使用。<strong>（不可以在其他定义积木下使用）</strong></p> \n<ol> \n <li><strong>返回</strong></li> \n</ol> \n<p><strong>函数的返回值，</strong><strong>可以返回0个或者1个数据</strong><strong>，可以输出和调用。</strong>&nbsp;</p> \n<p><strong>该积木只能在定义函数积木下使用</strong>&nbsp;</p> \n<p><strong>提示：</strong></p> \n<p>需要注意的是，在使用返回值的过程中，如果与条件判断结合，即“如果”“如果--否则”，则要<strong>全面考虑</strong>可能发生的情况。</p> \n<p>比如：我们想要角色Y坐标大于0的时候，返回所处位置的Y坐标值并显示出来。</p> \n<p>假设如果角色自己的Y坐标＞0，则返回自己的Y坐标值，点击运行会发现，系统显示报错信息：该函数有部分分支没有返回。（意思就是说：我们只设置了Y坐标＞0时，返回Y坐标值值，但是我们没有告诉系统，Y坐标＜0的时候该怎么做， 系统就会报错。）</p> \n<ol> \n <li><strong>函数调用</strong></li> \n</ol> \n<p>执行一次函数的调用，<strong>即执行对应函数名下的所有积木，并返回函数定义中设置的返回值。</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p> \n<p>如果函数定义中<strong>不存在返回值</strong>，积木盒子中也<strong>不会存在这块积木</strong>。&nbsp;</p> \n<p>提示：“置灰”处理&nbsp;</p> \n<p>大家在使用函数积木时，可能会不小心 删除/断开【定义函数】积木，导致的相关积木失效。&nbsp;所以，编程猫特意对函数积木做了“置灰”处理，提示积木失效，方便定位到问题。</p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1698579389,"created_at":1698579389,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"1668259","user":{"id":"1497430348","nickname":"大黄鸡111","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/codemaster/client/avatars//portrait_4.jpg","subject_id":21211,"work_shop_name":"大黄鸡工作室","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>当广播用</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1698572064,"created_at":1698572064,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"16910","user":{"id":"204645","nickname":"小假LittleFalse","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fqw3NfVBhmglR3dOjGtkKh5J2oXD","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>或者是找假·猫老祖</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1491020674,"created_at":1491020674,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"16902","user":{"id":"223645","nickname":"~断了个弦~","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FnwvON0WCp3LGI6ji-sbZlAJt06r","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>函数对于新手来说不是很常用，新手只需要了解基本积木就好</p>\n<p>另外：下次再有问题，请去找猫老祖……作为一个新手不需要知道太多超越性的积木，容易混乱……以后自然会上到那些方面的课程</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1491018987,"created_at":1491018987,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"16898","user":{"id":"194148","nickname":"MAlopos","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTk0MTQ4XzE5NDE0OF8xNjEzMzExNDQ1ODY5XzZlYmRkN2E0.jpeg","subject_id":615,"work_shop_name":"萌新院","work_shop_level":2,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>函数就是把好多积木合成一个积木</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1491002427,"created_at":1491002427,"earliest_comments":[]}],"offset":0,"limit":30,"total":6,"counted":true}